column5: looking for a company that I can buy the components to build spinner baits with. Any help will be greatly appreciated...Thanks
Try Luremaking.com - they have a lot of stuff
Go to www.jannsnetcraft.com ,You can order online or they have a free catalog they will send you,I think they are great to deal with and cheap too..Or call 1800-638-2723 to get there catalog...
Try reelbait.com he has some nice stuff and will work with you.
Go to Cabelas website and they have everything you need. Also, Gander Mountain has everything
